3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper discusses the efficient representation of conditional probability tables, which is relevant to data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - Bayesian networks can be used to model social networks and information flow, which is relevant to this sub-category.
